      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="b1dfeb52-5734-4ac3-a0b5-239c44b18731" type="Noun">
          <Vi>hầm (đường bộ, đường sắt, đường thủy, v.v.)</Vi>
          <En>A passage through or under something, especially through a mountain or under a road or river, typically for transport.</En>
          <Example>The train sped through the mountain tunnel in under two minutes.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="efe3ccfb-bb6f-41b5-a18c-d6bcb91d6b8f">
              <Vi>Xây dựng hoặc sử dụng hầm để vượt qua chướng ngại địa hình.</Vi>
              <En>Constructing or using a tunnel to bypass a natural or urban obstacle.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="295051bf-8854-40b1-9ac8-3a3cf5558a23">
              <Vi>Hệ thống giao thông đô thị sử dụng hầm để giảm ùn tắc.</Vi>
              <En>Urban transit systems use tunnels to reduce surface traffic congestion.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
        </Meaning>
